Our CapabilitiesVisions can become reality with the right advice, knowledge and plan to guide you forward

Wealth Planning
Your Vision, Our ExperienceDecisions made at every stage of your life can have long-lasting implications. We can help you evaluate your choices, as well as provide guidance to grow and preserve your wealth for all you envision now and in the future. 




				Thinking Through Essential Questions






					We have worked with countless individuals and families for over 200 years. This experience has taught us that while each person is unique, there are common goals and concerns.

					 



					We can help you think through these essential questions:



							Will I have enough to continue enjoying my lifestyle?



							What do I need to do to provide for my family and future generations?



							How can I best establish a philanthropic legacy?






Wealth Insights


 
 
	Partnering with your other professional advisors, we help implement strategies to preserve your wealth—so you can enjoy your lifestyle, provide for your family and support the causes most important to you. 
	Specifically, we can help you:


		Analyze projected outcomes to inform your decisions

		Evaluate risks to your wealth plan, including your spending rate, who you name as trustees and how you hold your assets

		Evaluate how to take advantage of your concentrated positions

		Plan for the succession and sale of your businesses

		Develop effective charitable-giving strategies

		Help execute your plan by serving as fiduciary



Protecting Your Legacy
	For over 200 years, wealthy individuals and their families have trusted J.P. Morgan to act as their trustee, co-trustee, agent or executor — ensuring their legacies are carried out as they intended.


	Trusts not only help transfer your wealth to family or charities according to your wishes, but also guide your beneficiaries as they manage and invest what they inherit. Our Trust Officers are available to work with you and your other professional advisors to evaluate your situation and deliver a strategy tailored to your unique needs. By serving as executor, we are prepared to assume the many responsibilities required in settling and managing complex estates.
													READ MORE 
The Philanthropy Centre at J.P. MorganThe Philanthropy Centre’s mission is to enhance philanthropic impact globally. Each member of The Philanthropy Centre’s dedicated team of senior advisors has 15 to 20 years of experience in the philanthropy and/or nonprofit sector.

The Philanthropy Centre guides clients through the many aspects of developing their philanthropic approach and effectively managing a private foundation. 
													READ MORE 
