Investing
Your Vision, Our Investment InsightsOur clients are building businesses, leading companies, pursuing passions. Part of their success is knowing the importance of having the right specialists in place when they need it.

As your partner in managing investments aligned with your vision, we continually identify potential opportunities and risks around the globe. We are able to implement these insights across all asset classes, including equities, fixed income, currencies and commodities, as well as our leading alternative investment platform.

Your J.P. Morgan investment portfolio can include managed and self-directed strategies. We can work with you to determine the right combination to develop an investment plan that’s purpose-built to achieve your wealth management goals.
A Comprehensive ViewEvery investment idea and portfolio strategy we recommend is anchored to a comprehensive view of world markets and macro-economic trends.
					 This view is informed by:


			Ongoing research in local markets around the world



			Thoughtful exchange of ideas among our global strategy teams on a daily basis



			In-depth analysis based on our forward-looking capital market assumptions (complex analysis of multiple market factors)



A Global Network, Local Strategies


 
 
	To implement our recommendations, we identify managers and investment strategies that are a sound fit for your investment plan.
 
	Our extensive global network allows us to:


		Source leading traditional and alternative managers and strategies from both J.P. Morgan and third-party firms

		Develop timely investment strategies

		Customize strategies to suit your individual needs and objectives




Global Institutional Wealth ManagementExclusively focused on family investment groups, we offer access to institutionally sophisticated insights, investments and solutions across JPMorgan Chase.

We bring you a heritage of experience partnering with generations of the world’s most successful families, helping address their distinct investment, governance and advisory needs.

													READ MORE 
The Endowments & Foundations GroupAs an advisor and investment manager, the Endowments & Foundations Group helps leaders of not-for-profit and charitable organizations address complex investment and financial management needs.

Through the Endowments & Foundations Group, you have access to a full spectrum of capabilities to help you meet the challenges of ensuring your organization is equipped with all the essential resources to accomplish its mission.

